I never took you for the sort of person who would show up in a kitchen, but I guess I was wrong.

You see a fridge. Now why would someone leave that there? You make out an oven! As if things weren't amazing enough already, you can even see a table. But the thing hasn't got anything on it. You see a counter. On the counter you see a roasted red hot pepper, a roasted red potato, a red apple, an orange bell pepper, a raw yellow potato, a cookbook and a knife.
